&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Highly skilled at building relationships with senior decision makers specifically in the Corporate Payments market; AP Manager, Controller, CFO, CEO, IT.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
