&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot; data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;As the Manager of Supplier Growth &amp;amp; Sales, you will lead a high-performing team of Supplier Account Managers &amp;amp; Retention Specialists dedicated to protecting &amp;amp; expanding the AvidXchange Payment Network. Your mission is to drive ePayment adoption and revenue growth by coaching your team to build deep, consultative relationships with our 1.3M+ supplier base. This leadership role that sits at the intersection of sales strategy, data analytics, and cross-functional advocacy, ensuring our suppliers realize maximum ROI from our automated payment solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
