&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Advocacy:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Customer Success, Product, and Marketing to resolve friction points in the supplier experience. You will serve as the &quot;voice of the supplier&quot; in strategic discussions to influence our product roadmap and operational enhancements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
